<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">Please generate a structured article based on the JSON Schema specification I provided, combined with the given topic content or specific data. The content of the article must strictly follow the output format and entity labeling requirements.</span></span>
